data.description:
Nestled in the a private neighborhood, this exquisite 2-year-old residence epitomizes modern comfort and tranquility. Boasting a generous layout, this home features four well-appointed bedrooms, offering ample space for family and guests alike. The two contemporary bathrooms are designed with sophistication in mind.

The heart of this home is undoubtedly its covered patio, which overlooks a lush, wooded backyard. This idyllic outdoor space invites relaxation and entertainment. The corner lot location further enhances the sense of privacy.

Practicality meets elegance with the inclusion of a spacious 2-car garage, ensuring convenience and security for your vehicles and storage needs.
